  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: CRITICAL CARE ACTIVITY CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A type of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_critical_care_activity">CRITICAL CARE ACTIVITY</xref>
 provided to a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 during a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_critical_care_period">CRITICAL CARE PERIOD</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>Note:</p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
National Codes 80-97 should not be reported nationally until the functionality to do so becomes available in the next release of the 
                <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/pages/help_pages/commissioning_data_sets_help.asp"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 and the associated XML Schema. Prior to this release, these codes must be recorded locally, however the National Codes 80-97 cannot be transmitted in the current version of the 
                <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/pages/help_pages/commissioning_data_sets_help.asp"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 (Version 6-2). Further guidance can be found on the 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
                <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/information-standards/information-standards-and-data-collections-including-extractions/publications-and-notifications/standards-and-collections/scci0075-neonatal-critical-care-minimum-data-set-version-2"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">SCCI0075</xref>
 and  
                <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/information-standards/information-standards-and-data-collections-including-extractions/publications-and-notifications/standards-and-collections/scci0076-paediatric-critical-care-minimum-data-set-version-2"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">SCCI0076</xref>
.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
